{"tid":2068449,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國研究發現一種類固醇可降新冠患者死亡率　世衛形容拯救生命突破","createTime":"2020-06-17T16:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T17:40:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"79684d18edefc555ed51098e1f803fb0c75a5ebd","tid":2068449,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532669-20200618.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532669-20200618.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wYhk9ljSbOzVJb7ECUhiv3w%3D&h=c9eb7514\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532669-20200618.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6c54e48e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532669-20200618.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n世衛組織歡迎英國研究發現，類固醇「地塞米松」有助減低新型冠狀病毒重症患者的死亡率，形容是「拯救生命的科技突破」。<br />\n<br />\n世衛總幹事譚德塞說，這是很好的消息，並祝賀英國政府、牛津大學、英國多間醫院和多名病人對研究的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n牛津大學的研究發現，用於治療炎症的「地塞米松」可以減低新型冠狀病毒重症患者的死亡率三分一。研究人員說，「地塞米松」本身價格便宜，而且可以立即使用。英國衛生大臣夏國賢說，將立即開始使用這種藥物治療新型肺炎患者。<br />\n<br />\n至今全球810萬人感染新型肺炎，接近44萬人死亡。"},{"pid":"fb1fba765f90f1473545db3d924fce86b21e014d","tid":2068449,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:43:44.000Z","msg":"英國研究"},{"pid":"05953ed2a83c07628482f9b172ea2a5fb807d636","tid":2068449,"uid":173630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:43:55.000Z","msg":"英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4c990666b2e0d7e54fc06ab40bd7756de0f14c","tid":2068449,"uid":37197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f370b4fb35c7e30134a3545aa6723706636b932","tid